# Mana Forge Context
- Main Entry: Java Spring Boot (mana-forge-api)
- Analysis Engine: Python FastAPI (mana-forge-engine)
- Frontend: React TypeScript (mana-forge-web)
- External Services: Strapi CMS (on Debian Server)
- Rules:
  - Java orchestrates all calls. 
  - Python is stateless (receives deck, returns analysis).
  - Use absolute types for MTG Premodern cards (4th Ed to Scourge).